  <br>
  (ii)	3x – 2y = 19----------------(2)
  <br>
  To make the coefficient of x the same; multiply equation (1) by 3 and equation (2) by 2
  <br>
  3 x 2x + 5y = 0
  <br>
  2 x 3x – 2y = 19
  <br>
  <strong>It becomes;</strong>
