  <span class='ml-5'>19y = ─38;</span> <strong><span class='ml-5'>19y = 15y ─(─4y)</strong> and <strong>−38 = 0 ─ 38</strong></span>
  <br>
  Divide both sides by 19
  <br>
  <sup>19y</sup>&frasl;<sub>19</sub> = <sup>−38</sup>&frasl;<sub>19</sub>
  <br>
  y = ─2
  <br>
